<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mạrạn ậtẖạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mạrạn ậtẖạ yạ yswʿ tʿwʿ tʿạl
 mạrạn ậtẖạ nḥn fy ạntẓạr
 lk qlwbnạ tsẖtạq tʿạl yạ yswʿ
 1- llạ̉bd ydwm mlkk tḥmynạ bymynk
 tqym ạlʿdl bḥkmk tʿạl yạ yswʿ
 2- ttẖmr ạlkẖyr fy sẖʿbnạ wạlslạm fy ạ̉rḍnạ
 mn bḥr lbḥr mjdk tʿạl yạ yswʿ
 3- tḥfẓ ạlṣgẖyr wạlfqyr trḥmn mn yṭlbk
 gẖạly tẖmnhm fy ʿynyk tʿạla yạ yswʿ</lyrics>
<hymn_number>9162</hymn_number>
<author>G. Du Boullay, G. Du Boullay</author>
</song>